parameters:
"This time it's a completely unknown building. It doesn't
seem like a mansion from this country either."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"Since it's also my first time seeing this building, let's
be careful as we proceed."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[24]
"Onee-san, I'm sorry for causing you trouble."\n<Saku>\F[8]\AA[FF]\FF[23]

"No, not at all. I don't think it's a bother in the
slightest."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[23]

"It's hard to see well... but it's sparkling and pretty,
isn't it?"\n<Saku>\F[1]\AA[FF]\FF[40]

"That's right... Hold on to this until we find where it can
be used, Saku."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[40]

"Little fox, you need not concern yourself with the use of
the key."\n<???>\F[1]\AA[FF]\FF[25]\AA[N]

"How dare you call my name so casually, insolent little
fox... Stand back!"\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[33]

"Hmm... Even a little fox is at the end of the line of gods.
I thought I had crushed that incarnate heart of yours..."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[35]

"Useless creatures who let it escape time and again. Those
who cannot even hunt a fox are of no use to me."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[37]
"Just by lightly touching that evil spirit..."\n<Yukine>\F[15]
"Now then... Saku. It's about time you returned to my side."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[38]

"It should be enough by now... You are my shrine maiden.
Stop frolicking with the likes of a little fox."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[38]

"What dissatisfies you, Saku... You can spend eternity in
this world. Without feeling sadness, pain, or anxiety, why
do you run? Do you intend to betray me?"\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[31]

"Come back, Saku. You, who were abandoned, belong by my
side."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[38]

"*cough*... To bind Saku in such a cold darkness, stripping
away all her senses so she can't feel anything..."\n<Yukine>\F[19]\AA[F]\FF[22]

"Do you have any idea how lonely Saku has been! Cursing so
many people, killing plenty with curses, leaving Saku all
alone in that world--You never cared about Saku at all."\n<Yukine>\F[19]\AA[F]\FF[23]
"You insolent creature... How dare a mere fox mock me."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[37]

"*gasp*, such a terrible curse. My throat, my skin is
burning."\n<Yukine>\F[15]\AA[F]\FF[26]

"Enough... I shall personally punish you. Once I skin you,
gouge out your eyes, and drag out your entrails, perhaps
Saku's heart will change."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[32]

"God... please stop... don't do horrible things to Onee-
san."\n<Saku>\F[15]\AA[FF]\FF[26]

"Ah, poor Saku. I will save you from the warmth soon. Just
wait a little longer."\n<Saku Disaster Moon>\FF[32]
(It seems like there's nothing here, just a layer of dust.)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here)
(I wonder if this key will fit...)
(Thank goodness, it looks like it fits)
(I wonder if there's anything else that might be useful)
(There's a picture of flowers on display.)
(...Looking at it makes my heart race.)
"Onee-chan... my body feels warm... I feel kind of strange."\n<Saku>\FF[23]
"Me too... Saku, let's rest here for a bit... haa haa"\n<Yukine>\F[9]\AA[F]\FF[23]
(A painting of a beautiful woman is on display.)
(I wonder if this key will fit...)
(Thank goodness, it looks like it fits)
